<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Life Timeline Portal</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Segoe UI,sans-serif;
}

body{
height:100vh;
overflow:hidden;
background:
linear-gradient(to bottom,#020617,#0f172a,#1e293b);
color:white;
}

.container{
height:100vh;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
gap:40px;
flex-wrap:wrap;
padding:20px;
}

/* PORTALS */

.portal{
width:180px;
height:320px;
border-radius:100px;
position:relative;
cursor:pointer;
transition:.5s;
overflow:hidden;
}

.portal::before{
content:"";
position:absolute;
inset:0;
border-radius:100px;
animation:glow 3s infinite alternate;
}

.portal:hover{
transform:translateY(-15px) scale(1.05);
}

@keyframes glow{

0%{
filter:brightness(1);
}

100%{
filter:brightness(1.5);
}

}

.blue::before{
background:
radial-gradient(circle,
#60a5fa,
#1d4ed8,
transparent 70%);
}

.purple::before{
background:
radial-gradient(circle,
#c084fc,
#7e22ce,
transparent 70%);
}

.green::before{
background:
radial-gradient(circle,
#34d399,
#047857,
transparent 70%);
}

.orange::before{
background:
radial-gradient(circle,
#fb923c,
#c2410c,
transparent 70%);
}

.gold::before{
background:
radial-gradient(circle,
#fde047,
#ca8a04,
transparent 70%);
}

/* TEXT */

.portal-content{
position:absolute;
bottom:30px;
width:100%;
text-align:center;
z-index:2;
}

.portal-content h2{
font-size:28px;
margin-bottom:8px;
}

.portal-content p{
font-size:14px;
color:#e2e8f0;
}

/* HEADING */

.heading{
position:absolute;
top:50px;
width:100%;
text-align:center;
}

.heading h1{
font-size:70px;
background:
linear-gradient(to right,
#60a5fa,
#c084fc,
#f472b6);
-webkit-background-clip:text;
-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
}

.heading p{
margin-top:15px;
font-size:20px;
color:#cbd5e1;
}

/* INFO PANEL */

.info{
position:absolute;
bottom:40px;
left:50%;
transform:translateX(-50%);
background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);
backdrop-filter:blur(15px);
padding:20px 40px;
border-radius:20px;
text-align:center;
width:70%;
max-width:700px;
}

.info h3{
margin-bottom:10px;
color:#93c5fd;
}

.info p{
line-height:1.8;
color:#e2e8f0;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="heading">
<h1>Life Timeline Portal</h1>
<p>Walk through the doors of your past, present and future.</p>
</div>

<div class="container">

<div class="portal blue">
<div class="portal-content">
<h2>Age 10</h2>
<p>Childhood</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="portal purple">
<div class="portal-content">
<h2>Age 18</h2>
<p>College</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="portal green">
<div class="portal-content">
<h2>Age 25</h2>
<p>Dream Career</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="portal orange">
<div class="portal-content">
<h2>Age 35</h2>
<p>Founder Era</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="portal gold">
<div class="portal-content">
<h2>Age 50</h2>
<p>Legacy</p>
</div>
</div>

</div>

<div class="info">
<h3>Your Story Is Still Being Written</h3>
<p>
Every portal represents a chapter of your life.
The future portals are empty because they're waiting
for the choices you make today.
</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
